-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Networking & Access
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| Azure Virtual Network (VNet)        | Core networking component for Azure.        					                   
| Network Security Groups (NSG)       | Firewall rules for VMs and subnets.         					                   
| Azure Bastion                       | Secure RDP/SSH to VMs without public IPs.   					                   
| Azure Load Balancer                 | Layer 4 traffic distribution.               					                   
| Azure Application Gateway           | Layer 7 load balancing + WAF.               					                                    
| Azure Front Door                    | Global traffic management with WAF and CDN. 					                   
| Azure DNS                           | DNS zone hosting and management.            					                   
| Private Link / Service Endpoints    | Private access to Azure PaaS services.      					                   
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Compute
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| Azure Virtual Machines (VMs)        | IaaS workloads; great for legacy or custom setups. 				               
| Azure App Service                   | PaaS hosting for web apps, APIs, etc.              				               
| Azure Functions                     | Serverless compute for event-driven tasks.         				               
| Azure Container Instances (ACI)     | Run containers without managing servers.           				               
| Azure Kubernetes Service (AKS)      | Managed Kubernetes for container orchestration.    				               
| VM Scale Sets (VMSS)                | Auto-scaling of virtual machine workloads.         				               
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Storage & DatabasesStorage & Databases
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| Azure Blob Storage                   | Scalable object storage (e.g., logs, images, backups). 			           
| Azure Files                          | File shares via SMB/NFS.                               			           
| Azure Disk Storage                   | High-performance persistent storage for VMs.           			           
| Azure Cosmos DB                      | Globally distributed NoSQL database.                   			           
| Azure SQL Database                   | Managed relational database service.                   			           
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Containers and Orchestration
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| Azure Kubernetes Service (AKS)       | Managed K8s clusters for deploying containerized apps. 			           
| Azure Container Registry (ACR)       | Private Docker registry for storing container images.  			           
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
CI/CD & DevOps
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| Azure DevOps                         | End-to-end DevOps tools: Repos, Pipelines, Boards, Artifacts, Test Plans.
| GitHub Actions (for Azure)           | Native GitHub CI/CD with Azure integrations.                             
| Azure Pipelines                      | Powerful build and release automation pipelines.                         
| Azure Artifacts                      | Package hosting for npm, Maven, NuGet, etc.                              
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Security & Identity
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| Microsoft Entra ID (Azure AD)        | Identity and access management.                 				                  
| Azure Key Vault                      | Securely store secrets, keys, and certificates. 				                  
| Managed Identities                   | Authentication without credentials.             				                  
| Azure Policy                         | Governance and compliance enforcement.          				                  
| Role-Based Access Control (RBAC)     | Fine-grained access permissions.                				                  
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Infrastructure as Code (IaC)
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| ARM Templates                        | Native JSON-based IaC templates.            					                    
| Bicep                                | Simplified language over ARM templates.     					                    
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Monitoring & Logging
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| Azure Monitor                        | Unified monitoring service for logs, metrics, alerts. 			              
| Azure Log Analytics                  | Log querying and visualization.                       			              
| Azure Application Insights           | Application performance monitoring (APM).             			              
| Network Watcher                      | Monitor and diagnose network traffic.                 			              
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Automation & Integration
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| Azure Automation                     | Runbooks, process automation, DSC configuration.                      	  
| Azure Logic Apps                     | Workflow automation connecting systems (low-code).                    	  
| Azure Event Grid                     | Event-based messaging and automation.                                   	
| Azure Service Bus                    | Reliable messaging between applications.                               	
| Azure Event Hubs                     | Real-time data streaming and ingestion.                                	
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Optional but Useful
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| Azure Blueprints                     | Package policies, ARM templates, and RBAC. 				                    	
| Azure Site Recovery                  | Disaster recovery.                         				                    	
| Azure Backup                         | Managed backup solution.                   			                    		
| Azure Cost Management                | Budgeting and cost tracking.               			                    		
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
